long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension helps you saving time by navigate through pages on Torah using chrome.
I put the most useful books i think a regular Yeshiva student will need, etc, תנ"ך, בבלי, ירושלמי, משנה, תוספתא, רי"ף, שו"ע, טור וכו'
